Phobia eyes Kluster, "That's true but the Trupredacus council still 
has it's loyal followers, I once saw a commander intenially overload 
his energeon circuits intentionally by thier orders, the explosion 
destroyed his entire unit and left his shoulders and head intact. He 
suffered in front of his base for ten cycles before shutting down. It 
was a mercifull fate compared to what they would have done if he 
hadn't followed orders." He thought back about thier meeting. "You've 
seen the firepower that the Iron Fist carries, what other purpose 
would a monstrosity such as that have?
